cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.RO, cs.CV 

The paper proposes a modular framework for learning complex tasks using multi-agent reinforcement learning with differentiable communication. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The paper also applies the proposed approach to model sensorimotor coordination, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of robotics (cs.RO) and computer vision (cs.CV).
